msgid "Linking related datasets"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-data.adoc:188
msgid "Some datasets may come from the same research project or may be related in certain context. The current recommendation is to link them using a project identifier."
